{"tid":752775,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"留言正皮功能應否存在？","createTime":"2018-07-23T05:32:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T08:53:04.000Z","uid":76420,"like":19,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3b0b112038e97ac10eeea8c1ea81ebe6921552df","tid":752775,"uid":76420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:32:20.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有冇試過見到有啲留言比人感覺半信半疑、貌似正路，但見到多正皮就信以為真？見到多負皮就以為唔可信？ 留言正負皮會唔會存在住誤導成份？特別係而家越黎越少人缺乏獨立思考，冇諗過但見到多正皮多就信。<br />\n<br />\n再者，留言正皮會唔會影響討論？而家連登都不難發現一啲會員為左正皮而留啲與討論無關嘅幽默性、諷刺性留言，影響左討論。當然，長遠黎講係有心討論嘅就唔會有問題。<br />\n<br />\n第三，可能有少少陰謀論。其實正皮數可以搵人洗翻黎，多啲正皮可以令到個留言看似公信力or可信性高啲，特別係而家申請ac門檻咁低，洗高正皮數相信唔難。<br />\n<br />\n見過咁多討論區係得連登寧舍有個留言正皮功能，好古怪<br />\n<br />\nps，純粹客觀討論，想睇下大家意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a6857780be6c4f69827197cc827f5c79492b81","tid":752775,"uid":76420,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:47:57.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc2278b32443cbf5eef08ab520ecd344cd33e6c","tid":752775,"uid":105480,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:48:33.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"0d5198bf46b02fd79b3f9b0e764f0cee172c2f6c","tid":752775,"uid":76420,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bc2278b32443cbf5eef08ab520ecd344cd33e6c","tid":752775,"uid":105480,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:48:33.000Z","msg":"閱"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8251abd5966eb95093e1c266c845e96b5bd4d500","tid":752775,"uid":76420,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0d5198bf46b02fd79b3f9b0e764f0cee172c2f6c","tid":752775,"uid":76420,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bc2278b32443cbf5eef08ab520ecd344cd33e6c","tid":752775,"uid":105480,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T05:48:33.000Z","msg":"閱"},"cite